### 5.6 GET Daily Collection Records - Admin (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 5.7 GET Daily Collection Records - Resource Management (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}

###

### 5.8 GET Daily Collection Records - Worker (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}

###

### 5.9 GET Daily Collection Records - Visitor (Expect 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records
Authorization: Bearer {{visitorToken}}

###

### 5.10 GET Daily Collection Record By Id - Worker (Expect 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records/1
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}

###

### 5.11 POST Daily Collection Record - Worker (Expect 201 or 200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campId": 1,
  "personId": 1,
  "resourceTypeId": 1,
  "date": "2024-01-01",
  "expectedAmount": "1000",
  "actualAmount": "950",
  "differenceReason": "string",
  "recordedBy": 2,
  "movementId": null
}

###

### 5.12 POST Daily Collection Record - Resource Management (Expect 201 or 200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campId": 1,
  "personId": 1,
  "resourceTypeId": 1,
  "date": "2024-01-02",
  "expectedAmount": "8.00",
  "actualAmount": "8.00",
  "differenceReason": null,
  "recordedBy": 3,
  "movementId": null
}

###

### 5.13 PUT Daily Collection Record - Worker (Expect 200)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records/1
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actualAmount": "970",
  "differenceReason": "field correction"
}

###

### 5.14 PUT Daily Collection Record - Resource Management (Expect 200)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records/1
Authorization: Bearer {{resourceToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "differenceReason": "official validated reason"
}

###

### 5.15 DELETE Daily Collection Record - Admin (Expect 403 ForbiddenException Audit)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 5.16 GET Daily Collection Records - Travel Manager (Expect 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/daily-collection-records
Authorization: Bearer {{travelToken}}